data.body:
We have a content project containing both normal content (e.g. .png) as well as some non standard files which are just copied (.level)

If I multi select .PNG files and .Level files we get a crash

in pipelinetypes.cs

```
    public override bool Equals(object obj)
    {
        var other = obj as ImporterTypeDescription;
        if (other == null)
            return false;

        return this.TypeName.Equals(other.TypeName);  <<--- other.TypeName is null
    }
```

I feel the solution is to return false if other.TypeName is null but I dont know enough about this code to be sure. Seems to work though.

e.g. 
    if (other == null || other.TypeName == null || this.TypeName == null)
           return false;

